OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782224343
OL,3,CTwo young men admit carrying out cyber
OL,4,Cattack on Transport for London
OL,6,FThey had denied conspiring together to
OL,7,Fcommit unauthorised acts against TfL
OL,8,Fbetween August 29 2024 and September 6
OL,9,F2024, but changed their pleas at
OL,10,FWoolwich Crown Court on Monday, before
OL,11,Ftheir trial was due to begin.
OL,13,FThe attack posed "significant risk" to
OL,14,Fthe UK economy and London residents,
OL,15,Fprosecutors said previously.
OL,26,@uD@ROUuD@cO]
