CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782224343
OL,3,CTwo young men admit carrying out cyber
OL,4,Cattack on Transport for London
OL,6,FFlowers, of Walsall, West Midlands,
OL,7,Fwho was first arrested over the TfL
OL,8,Fattack in September 2024 and then
OL,9,Farrested again in September last year,
OL,10,Falso admitted targeting US healthcare
OL,11,Ffirms.
OL,13,FHe pleaded guilty to conspiring with
OL,14,Fothers to commit unauthorised acts
OL,15,Fagainst SSM Health Care Corporation
OL,16,Fand attempting to commit unauthorised
OL,17,Facts against Sutter Health.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
