CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1782224343
OL,3,CTwo young men admit carrying out cyber
OL,4,Cattack on Transport for London
OL,6,FJubair, from Tower Hamlets, east
OL,7,FLondon, faced an additional charge
OL,8,Funder the Regulation of Investigatory
OL,9,FPowers Act of failing to disclose the
OL,10,FPin or passwords of his devices but
OL,11,Fthat was left to lie on the file.
OL,13,FThe pair will be sentenced at the same
OL,14,Fcourt on July 15 and 16.
